<h1>Thank You for Applying!</h1>

<p>Dear <%= @candidate.first_name %>,</p>

<p>
  Thank you for your interest in the <strong><%= @job.title %></strong> position at
  <strong><%= @organization.name %></strong>. We have received your application and
  our recruiting team will review it shortly.
</p>

<h2>What's Next?</h2>

<p>
  Our team will carefully review your application and qualifications. If your background
  matches our requirements, we will reach out to schedule the next steps in our interview process.
</p>

<h2>Track Your Application</h2>

<p>
  You can check the status of your application at any time using the link below:
</p>

<p style="margin: 20px 0;">
  <%= link_to "View Application Status", @status_url, style: "background-color: #0d6efd; color: white; padding: 12px 24px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 4px;" %>
</p>

<p>
  <strong>Your tracking code:</strong> <code><%= @application.tracking_token %></code>
</p>

<p>
  Save this code - you can use it to check your status at any time by visiting our
  <%= link_to "application status page", application_status_url %>.
</p>

<h2>Application Details</h2>

<table style="width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse;">
  <tr>
    <td style="padding: 8px; border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;"><strong>Position:</strong></td>
    <td style="padding: 8px; border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;"><%= @job.title %></td>
  </tr>
  <% if @job.department %>
    <tr>
      <td style="padding: 8px; border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;"><strong>Department:</strong></td>
      <td style="padding: 8px; border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;"><%= @job.department.name %></td>
    </tr>
  <% end %>
  <tr>
    <td style="padding: 8px; border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;"><strong>Location:</strong></td>
    <td style="padding: 8px; border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;"><%= @job.location.presence || @job.location_type_display %></td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td style="padding: 8px; border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;"><strong>Applied:</strong></td>
    <td style="padding: 8px; border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;"><%= @application.applied_at.strftime("%B %d, %Y") %></td>
  </tr>
</table>

<p style="margin-top: 30px;">
  Thank you for considering a career with <%= @organization.name %>. We appreciate your interest
  and will be in touch soon.
</p>

<p>
  Best regards,<br>
  The <%= @organization.name %> Recruiting Team
</p>
